9}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's Decathlon and a handful of qualifying rounds kept fans entertained until the men's 10,000m final brought the house down over the final event of the night.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.804779569449199e-67, \"text\": \"Decathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decathlon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a handful\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying rounds\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 10,000m\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the final event\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the morning session saw the opening rounds of the women's 100m and men's 1,500m, the afternoon slate was gifted the women's 800m and 5,000m heats, as well as an Olympic record-breaking men's 10,000m, which put an exclamation point on the first day of competition.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning session\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening rounds\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 100m\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"men's 1,500m\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"the afternoon slate\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 800m\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"5,000m heats\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic record-breaking men's 10,000m\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"an exclamation point\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the first day\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tomorrow's morning session begins bright and early at 4:05 a.m. EST with the men's Decathlon 110mH.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tomorrow's morning session\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"4:05 a.m.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"EST\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's Decathlon\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saturday's afternoon session is set to kick off at 1:10 p.m. EST and will include four finals in the men's shot put, women's triple jump and 100m, as well as the mixed 4x400m and the decathlon 1,500m, which is the conclusion to the 10-event contest.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday's afternoon session\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"1:10 p.m.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"four finals\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's shot put\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"women's triple jump\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"100m\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed 4x400m\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"the decathlon\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"1,500m\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the conclusion\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10-event contest\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are someone who likes a little bit of chaos over the course of 12.5 laps, the opening round of the women's 5,000m was not for you.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"chaos\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"12.5 laps\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening round\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 5,000m\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As we expected, the favorites ran their own race and comfortably made their way to the final.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the favorites\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"their own race\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kenya's Faith Kipyegon, the second fastest woman of all-time led the way for all 16 qualifiers in 14:57.65.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999979554559, \"rank\": 1.6117687907220942e-09, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Faith Kipyegon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second fastest woman\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"all-time\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"all 16 qualifiers\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seven other women were right behind Kipyegon in the first heat, as Netherland's Sifan Hassan and Italy's Nadi Battocletti both crossed in 14:57.65.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sifan Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wiki