inal\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really wanted to perform well, especially the way I was selected for the Olympics,\\\" Morgan said afterward.\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\", \"score\": 0.6738498221481815, \"rank\": 0.48396539565522373, \"text\": \"Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kind of wanted to kind of prove that I belong to be here, since I did not get the top three spots.\\\"\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top three spots\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following a pair of top-two finishes in the long jump and shot put, Germany's Leo Neugebauer -- the collegiate record-holder for Texas -- heads back to the Olympic Village on top of the decathlon leaderboard and just 42 points in front of Ayden Owens-Delerme, who is representing Puerto Rico.\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2638, \"end\": 2645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5855599572312309, \"rank\": 0.704953045065516, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2648, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9820836846753098, \"rank\": 0.018243027609400657, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 2652, \"